com.example.macie.mobilecheckout.program_logic

Class VirtualBasket

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.macie.mobilecheckout.program_logic.VirtualBasket

  • public class VirtualBasket
extends java.lang.Object
    Implements lazy instantiation design pattern for singleton classes. Preserves list of Product objects inside LinkedList. Allows for additional and removal of the list content.
